commit.message:
update changelog for 1.10.1

Signed-off-by: Stuart Halloway <stu@cognitect.com>

CLJ-2504 More options to configure error reporting

Signed-off-by: Stuart Halloway <stu@cognitect.com>

CLJ-2497 - Print error report location on its own line

Signed-off-by: Stuart Halloway <stu@cognitect.com>

CLJ-2499 Compiler expr eval methods should not report as compiler errors

Signed-off-by: Stuart Halloway <stu@cognitect.com>

CLJ-2484 Move user.clj initialization out of RT<clinit>

Signed-off-by: Stuart Halloway <stu@cognitect.com>

CLJ-2463 - clojure.main uncaught exception handling

Add err->msg helper to capture exception print pipeline.
Add :clojure.error/path to ex-triage output.
Change ex-str message loc from name to path.
On uncaught exception, print nice exception, print full data to tmp dir, exit with return code 1.
Add main option --report-stderr to force print to stderr.

Signed-off-by: Stuart Halloway <stu@cognitect.com>

CLJ-2491 - Make fragile tests work under Java 12 and less fragile

Signed-off-by: Stuart Halloway <stu@cognitect.com>

CLJ-2454 When reflectively finding a matching method, also check whether the method is module accessible to call, and if not use an accessible super method

Signed-off-by: Stuart Halloway <stu@cognitect.com>

CLJ-2449 Make serialized-require private

Signed-off-by: Stuart Halloway <stu@cognitect.com>

CLJ-2447 clojure.datafy docstring is misplaced

Signed-off-by: Stuart Halloway <stu@cognitect.com>

CLJ-2448 Change async-require to serialized-require
